1
00:00:09,021 --> 00:00:10,045
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,395 --> 00:00:19,023
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:20,065 --> 00:00:22,226
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,902 --> 00:00:26,564
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,672 --> 00:00:30,300
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32,010 --> 00:00:35,104
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,747 --> 00:00:38,875
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,352 --> 00:00:44,721
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,359 --> 00:00:49,122
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,227 --> 00:00:50,956
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:51,029 --> 00:00:53,361
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:56,663
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,735 --> 00:00:58,635
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,703 --> 00:01:01,137
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03,041 --> 00:01:09,605
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,715 --> 00:01:13,206
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,985 --> 00:01:16,852
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,693 --> 00:01:22,990
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,464 --> 00:01:26,988
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,784
<i>This is good!</i>

21
00:01:44,861 --> 00:01:47,329
<i>Bit by bit,</i>
<i>I'm figuring out the timing...</i>

22
00:01:53,469 --> 00:01:54,936
<i>He read my movement.</i>

23
00:01:55,538 --> 00:01:57,233
<i>No way could he do that!</i>

24
00:01:58,174 --> 00:02:00,870
Darn!
We were so close!

25
00:02:00,943 --> 00:02:03,411
Naruto, can you still move?

26
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:06,944
Of course! I'm totally fine!

27
00:02:07,817 --> 00:02:10,843
<i>He's pretty much spent...</i>
<i>and it's no wonder.</i>

28
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,982
<i>Shadow Clone Jutsu uses</i>
<i>a lot of Chakra.</i>

29
00:02:14,724 --> 00:02:16,954
<i>But thanks to him,</i>
<i>we found our way out.</i>

30
00:02:17,994 --> 00:02:19,222
<i>I found the way to break through!</i>

31
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,725
<i>Hah! Impossible!</i>

32
00:02:24,834 --> 00:02:27,928
<i>That was just a coincidence.</i>

33
00:02:31,841 --> 00:02:33,035
Naruto! Run!

34
00:02:33,810 --> 00:02:36,438
Run out of here and
attack from the outside!

35
00:02:37,513 --> 00:02:39,242
A-All right!

36
00:02:41,350 --> 00:02:42,578
You won't be able to...!

37
00:02:55,298 --> 00:02:56,697
I-I'm not going to lose!

38
00:02:59,769 --> 00:03:00,599
There!

39
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:02,638
Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!

40
00:03:29,031 --> 00:03:30,464
Darn!

41
00:03:31,801 --> 00:03:32,995
T-That was good just now!

42
00:03:33,069 --> 00:03:33,831
What?

43
00:03:34,637 --> 00:03:36,127
We're doing it one more time!

44
00:03:37,473 --> 00:03:38,667
All right!

45
00:03:42,311 --> 00:03:45,337
<i>It's likely that there's a limit</i>
<i>to that guy's Chakra, too!</i>

46
00:03:46,349 --> 00:03:47,748
<i>To prove that,</i>
<i>he's little by little...</i>

47
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:56,888
<i>This won't go as you've planned.</i>

48
00:03:58,227 --> 00:03:59,694
<i>First, I'll get you!</i>

49
00:04:05,501 --> 00:04:06,468
Sasuke!

50
00:04:15,778 --> 00:04:20,272
<i>Darn! It's been a while since</i>
<i>I've fought in such bad conditions.</i>

51
00:04:22,084 --> 00:04:24,712
<i>And I'm worried about</i>
<i>Sasuke and Naruto, too...</i>

52
00:04:28,424 --> 00:04:34,226
<i>Be calm...Think...</i>
<i>What will he come after?</i>

53
00:04:35,064 --> 00:04:36,622
<i>Oh no!</i>

54
00:04:52,615 --> 00:04:53,240
What?!

55
00:04:53,549 --> 00:04:54,573
Too late!

56
00:05:05,461 --> 00:05:12,094
<i>The Broken Seal</i>

57
00:05:14,503 --> 00:05:16,664
<i>That was Sakura's voice!</i>

58
00:05:17,607 --> 00:05:18,835
<i>Did something happen?</i>

59
00:05:19,976 --> 00:05:22,035
<i>What's that Kakashi doing?</i>

60
00:05:25,481 --> 00:05:27,676
Sa... kura...

61
00:05:28,351 --> 00:05:30,478
<i>Darn it... I must do something...</i>

62
00:05:33,889 --> 00:05:35,914
I'll do something about it...

63
00:05:37,093 --> 00:05:38,560
<i>T-This guy...</i>

64
00:05:39,195 --> 00:05:40,787
Here I go...

65
00:05:43,165 --> 00:05:44,564
It's pointless to struggle.

66
00:06:01,117 --> 00:06:02,414
Naruto, behind you!!

67
00:06:07,490 --> 00:06:08,252
Naruto!

68
00:06:08,991 --> 00:06:12,483
It's impossible for you
to get out of here.

69
00:06:13,462 --> 00:06:14,929
I mean it.

70
00:06:16,465 --> 00:06:18,057
Can you stand up, Naruto?

71
00:06:18,234 --> 00:06:20,031
Y-Yeah...

72
00:06:20,236 --> 00:06:22,101
From now on,
don't waste your Chakra!

73
00:06:22,371 --> 00:06:24,032
You're playing right into his hands.

74
00:06:25,741 --> 00:06:27,606
I know.

75
00:06:29,245 --> 00:06:30,303
<i>Darn it!</i>

76
00:06:30,379 --> 00:06:32,472
<i>If things continue like this,</i>
<i>it's going to be really bad.</i>

77
00:06:32,882 --> 00:06:33,906
<i>I...</i>

78
00:06:33,983 --> 00:06:35,917
<i>I have to do something.</i>

79
00:06:38,988 --> 00:06:41,047
<i>Strangely, my eyes have adjusted...</i>

80
00:06:41,791 --> 00:06:45,318
It's about the time I put
an end to this for you...

81
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,029
<i>What?!</i>

82
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:56,361
Stand up, you idiot!

83
00:06:59,275 --> 00:07:04,542
<i>I'm aiming for a vital spot...</i>
<i>but he's parrying all of them.</i>

84
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:11,044
I know...
you're so persistent!

85
00:07:16,792 --> 00:07:19,488
<i>A coincidence...</i>
<i>No, that's not it.</i>

86
00:07:19,929 --> 00:07:25,128
<i>On the contrary, he's fighting</i>
<i>while covering for his friend.</i>

87
00:07:28,437 --> 00:07:30,132
<i>Surely, my movements...</i>

88
00:07:31,974 --> 00:07:35,535
<i>That boy...he can see something.</i>

89
00:07:37,146 --> 00:07:38,443
<i>What in the world...?</i>

90
00:07:39,615 --> 00:07:41,139
<i>Okay, in that case...</i>

91
00:07:42,485 --> 00:07:43,509
He disappeared.

92
00:07:43,586 --> 00:07:45,781
Where, where did he disappear to?!

93
00:07:46,455 --> 00:07:48,514
Naruto! Don't faint!

94
00:07:48,991 --> 00:07:51,459
I can't take care of you
any more than I am now!

95
00:07:52,161 --> 00:07:54,459
Who asked you to take care of me...

96
00:07:57,900 --> 00:08:01,996
It seems that kid has
reached his limits.

97
00:08:08,210 --> 00:08:08,938
Tsk...

98
00:08:09,011 --> 00:08:12,208
Amazing...
That's an amazing move.

99
00:08:13,516 --> 00:08:15,245
You move well...

100
00:08:15,885 --> 00:08:16,681
Wha?!

101
00:08:17,653 --> 00:08:19,553
But I'll stop you
with the next one.

102
00:08:21,023 --> 00:08:22,149
Motor function...

103
00:08:22,725 --> 00:08:26,286
Reflexes...
Ability to judge a situation...

104
00:08:27,897 --> 00:08:32,459
All of these things...
should be at their limits!

105
00:08:34,937 --> 00:08:35,733
<i>He's coming!</i>

106
00:08:38,073 --> 00:08:39,062
<i>Calm down...</i>

107
00:08:40,242 --> 00:08:41,470
<i>Focus!</i>

108
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,938
<i>And...</i>
<i>See everything!</i>

109
00:08:59,195 --> 00:09:00,355
He saw through absolutely everything?!

110
00:09:01,831 --> 00:09:02,661
No way...

111
00:09:14,677 --> 00:09:15,575
Those eyes...

112
00:09:16,378 --> 00:09:17,402
It can't be...

113
00:09:19,915 --> 00:09:20,904
Sharingan...

114
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,012
You are...

115
00:09:26,722 --> 00:09:28,053
Only a little, but...

116
00:09:29,291 --> 00:09:30,519
I was able to see!

117
00:09:32,828 --> 00:09:36,423
So, you also have the power
of Kekkei Genkai...

118
00:09:38,634 --> 00:09:39,794
<i>What a kid...</i>

119
00:09:40,636 --> 00:09:41,967
<i>It's not perfect yet,</i>

120
00:09:42,905 --> 00:09:46,033
<i>but to think that in the middle of a battle</i>
<i>he was able to rouse this power...</i>

121
00:09:48,177 --> 00:09:51,669
<i>If that's the case,</i>
<i>I can't fight him too long...</i>

122
00:09:52,915 --> 00:09:55,281
<i>This Jutsu uses a lot of Chakra.</i>

123
00:09:55,985 --> 00:09:58,783
<i>There are also limits to retaining</i>
<i>the teleportation speed.</i>

124
00:09:59,788 --> 00:10:03,155
<i>Besides, the longer the fight continues,</i>

125
00:10:03,659 --> 00:10:07,789
<i>the more my movements will enter</i>
<i>into the range of his "reading."</i>

126
00:10:09,532 --> 00:10:13,798
<i>In fact, his eyes</i>
<i>have already captured me.</i>

127
00:10:17,406 --> 00:10:20,068
<i>It would be foolish to aim</i>
<i>straight at him.</i>

128
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:22,334
<i>In that case...</i>

129
00:10:24,513 --> 00:10:27,414
<i>I'll use that kid to lure him in!</i>

130
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,715
What?!

131
00:10:32,488 --> 00:10:33,420
Let me make it in time!

132
00:10:47,169 --> 00:10:48,602
K- Kakashi Sensei!

133
00:10:49,004 --> 00:10:52,235
You were late entering
to guard, Kakashi.

134
00:10:52,775 --> 00:10:57,212
Your whole-hearted intent to help
those kids has gone to your head,

135
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:59,747
and it seems to have clouded
your Sharingan

136
00:10:59,815 --> 00:11:01,476
with even heavier fog.

137
00:11:02,618 --> 00:11:05,519
Even though you have
those impressive eyes,

138
00:11:05,654 --> 00:11:08,987
your ability to read your enemy's
movements is getting cloudy.

139
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:14,323
Amuse me more, Kakashi...

140
00:11:15,331 --> 00:11:18,391
I want to repay my debt in
an amusing way.

141
00:11:19,835 --> 00:11:26,206
Don't worry. Anytime now,
Haku is going to defeat those kids.

142
00:11:34,116 --> 00:11:37,244
You better apologize to them
in tears

143
00:11:37,319 --> 00:11:41,415
when you are in "the next world"
for your lack of strength.

144
00:12:11,487 --> 00:12:14,388
Sasuke will be defeated...?

145
00:12:16,459 --> 00:12:17,585
That's not true!

146
00:12:18,561 --> 00:12:19,585
Sasuke is...

147
00:12:19,896 --> 00:12:20,920
<i>Cha!</i>

148
00:12:22,198 --> 00:12:23,222
Not by that guy!

149
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,260
<i>Cha!</i>

150
00:12:25,969 --> 00:12:27,129
He won't be defeated!

151
00:12:28,204 --> 00:12:29,762
<i>Cha!</i>

152
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,137
Naruto won't either!

153
00:12:33,243 --> 00:12:34,369
That's right.

154
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,272
Huh!

155
00:12:37,947 --> 00:12:42,816
I... believe in their strength.

156
00:12:45,221 --> 00:12:49,681
Naruto is the Number One Hyperactive,
Knucklehead Ninja...

157
00:12:51,394 --> 00:12:53,658
And Sasuke is a member of
the most excellent clan

158
00:12:53,730 --> 00:12:56,198
in the Hidden Leaf Village!

159
00:12:57,767 --> 00:12:58,791
That can't be!

160
00:13:00,136 --> 00:13:04,300
Yes...
His name is Sasuke Uchiha...

161
00:13:05,675 --> 00:13:07,905
He bears within his body...

162
00:13:07,977 --> 00:13:10,537
the famous Kekkei Genkai
of the Uchiha clan!

163
00:13:11,381 --> 00:13:12,905
He's a Ninja genius.

164
00:13:15,451 --> 00:13:19,547
He's the remaining survivor
of that tragic clan?!

165
00:13:27,964 --> 00:13:30,489
No wonder he grows so quickly.

166
00:13:33,202 --> 00:13:33,998
But...

167
00:13:34,837 --> 00:13:37,362
That's the same as Haku.

168
00:13:39,042 --> 00:13:42,136
Nobody has ever beaten
that secret Jutsu of Haku's

169
00:13:43,313 --> 00:13:45,178
Not one person in the past...

170
00:13:48,017 --> 00:13:49,450
Well then...

171
00:13:49,819 --> 00:13:52,549
It's about time I settled this too, huh.

172
00:13:52,989 --> 00:13:55,116
Sakura, don't move from here.

173
00:13:55,291 --> 00:13:57,816
Uh... ah... okay!

174
00:14:04,634 --> 00:14:07,967
No, <i>I'm</i> going to put
an end to this!

175
00:14:18,281 --> 00:14:20,249
For God's sake, you...

176
00:14:21,351 --> 00:14:25,378
just won't quit...
dragging my feet, will you?

177
00:14:26,022 --> 00:14:27,455
You did it!
Sasuke...!

178
00:14:42,605 --> 00:14:44,573
W-What kind of expression
is that...

179
00:14:45,375 --> 00:14:50,506
You... idiot...!

180
00:14:51,914 --> 00:14:53,882
W-Why?!

181
00:14:55,685 --> 00:14:57,880
You protected me...?!

182
00:14:59,022 --> 00:15:03,618
How the hell... should I know?

183
00:15:25,314 --> 00:15:29,978
<i>Sasuke...! Sasuke...! Sasuke...!</i>

184
00:15:35,391 --> 00:15:36,551
Hmph...

185
00:15:38,361 --> 00:15:39,555
You...

186
00:15:40,663 --> 00:15:42,324
I hated you...

187
00:15:44,634 --> 00:15:47,660
Why? Why...?

188
00:15:48,337 --> 00:15:50,805
Why... me...?

189
00:15:57,980 --> 00:16:00,107
I didn't ask for your help!!

190
00:16:04,787 --> 00:16:06,311
I don't know...

191
00:16:06,823 --> 00:16:11,123
My body moved... of its own accord...

192
00:16:12,061 --> 00:16:13,050
Fool!

193
00:16:26,242 --> 00:16:27,300
Sasuke!

194
00:16:29,312 --> 00:16:30,904
That man...

195
00:16:34,183 --> 00:16:37,619
Until I defeated... my brother...

196
00:16:40,423 --> 00:16:42,357
I absolutely refused to die...

197
00:16:42,425 --> 00:16:44,893
That's what I decided, but...

198
00:16:50,766 --> 00:16:54,634
You, don't die...

199
00:17:31,073 --> 00:17:31,937
He...

200
00:17:44,387 --> 00:17:46,719
To protect someone dear to him...

201
00:17:48,224 --> 00:17:51,318
he would plunge in
knowing it was a trap...

202
00:17:52,528 --> 00:17:56,862
He's a Shinobi worthy of respect.

203
00:17:59,468 --> 00:18:02,130
Is this the first time you faced
a friend's death?

204
00:18:03,406 --> 00:18:06,068
This is the way of the Shinobi...

205
00:18:11,414 --> 00:18:12,881
Shut up!

206
00:18:16,886 --> 00:18:21,949
<i>Even though I...</i>
<i>hated you too...</i>

207
00:18:31,867 --> 00:18:33,425
I won't forgive you...

208
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:56,155
I'm going to kill you!

209
00:19:05,568 --> 00:19:07,365
<i>What is this Chakra?!</i>

210
00:19:11,874 --> 00:19:13,068
<i>It can't be...</i>

211
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,505
<i>For Chakras to be tangible like that...</i>

212
00:19:18,314 --> 00:19:22,444
<i>A-And...what a ghastly Chakra that is...</i>

213
00:19:36,799 --> 00:19:40,530
<i>The wound on his hand...</i>
<i>It's healing instantly...</i>

214
00:19:42,171 --> 00:19:43,536
<i>This boy...</i>

215
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:45,664
<i>Who in hell is he...?</i>

216
00:19:56,385 --> 00:19:57,374
Is it Zabuza...?

217
00:19:58,888 --> 00:19:59,684
No!

218
00:20:00,056 --> 00:20:02,251
This sinister Chakra was once...

219
00:20:04,860 --> 00:20:05,792
It can't be!

220
00:20:06,462 --> 00:20:08,453
What is... this Chakra?

221
00:20:09,131 --> 00:20:10,689
It feels foul...

222
00:20:11,334 --> 00:20:15,828
Kakashi?
No, it's too big to be Kakashi's...

223
00:20:17,340 --> 00:20:18,307
Who is it?

224
00:20:20,976 --> 00:20:22,000
Naruto!

225
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:31,445
<i>Oh no...</i>

226
00:20:33,756 --> 00:20:35,018
<i>At the time like this...</i>

227
00:20:35,424 --> 00:20:36,686
<i>The seal has broken...?</i>

228
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:38,820
<i>I have to hurry!</i>

229
00:21:14,063 --> 00:21:15,121
<i>He's coming!</i>

230
00:22:55,166 --> 00:22:56,360
How dare you!

231
00:22:56,434 --> 00:23:00,803
You ruined Sasuke!
Damn you!

232
00:23:01,806 --> 00:23:03,501
Sasuke's dream...

233
00:23:06,644 --> 00:23:07,872
What about dream?!

234
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:11,308
Darn you! Darn you! Darn you!

235
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:14,514
Because of your dream!

236
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:19,383
Next time:
"The White Past: Hidden Ambition"
